          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card-icon">🏡</div>
        <h3>Low-Maintenance Homes</h3>
        <p>Most 55+ communities handle exterior upkeep, landscaping, and common area maintenance through HOA fees — freeing you from weekend chores and letting you focus on living.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="what-card">
        <div style="height:160px;background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576013551627-0cc20b96c2a7?w=600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;margin:-44px -40px 20px;position:relative">
